    <h1>Side Quests</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p local-id=3D"c3f9cd1ab35c"><strong><u>GenAI Adoption Survey</u></=
strong></p>
<p class=3D"media-group"><img height=3D"250" style=3D"margin: 2px; border: =
1px solid #ddd; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: text-bottom;" src=
=3D"bbee80d7488fef7489dd0f98e33f1c3bdb6d5d0bf753bdf82b2c0938483b0530" width=
=3D"250"></p>
<p local-id=3D"42de5299d9e8"><strong><u>BAU weekday patching</u></strong></=
p>
<ul local-id=3D"1a821f448dee">
<li local-id=3D"b157855548dd">
<p local-id=3D"e349e5a17419">AGREED: Non-Prod system patching can be done o=
n weekdays</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"63aeb9ca136f">
<p local-id=3D"482381c7b2c3">In-Progress</p>
<ul local-id=3D"d3c48a62a6aa">
<li local-id=3D"7d1b981a890c">
<p local-id=3D"664f19dc5674">Non-Gold and no batch impact systems are being=
 identified for weekday patching</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8251c3612274">
<p local-id=3D"45f071a17c07">Weekday patch timing will be agreed with App O=
wner and the Business</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"cd2c09a63fb4">
<p local-id=3D"1e268b550518">Osama-san will send weekday patching requireme=
nts for 4 MPS Guardia Print Servers, maintained by FujiFilm (Done). <strong=
>In-progress</strong>: set patch timing and registration for weekday patchi=
ng.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c6e169ef078f">
<p local-id=3D"ccc574ebc92a">Pull all systems that are not on the main list=
 (David)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"5e73ccf2da85"><strong><u>Approval workflow optimization - </=
u></strong><a data-card-appearance=3D"inline" href=3D"https://manulife-ets.=
atlassian.net/wiki/x/kgAkyQM" local-id=3D"cb3031bb1c47" rel=3D"nofollow">ht=
tps://manulife-ets.atlassian.net/wiki/x/kgAkyQM</a></p>
<ul local-id=3D"5bd70d82737b">
<li local-id=3D"795e3028667e">
<p local-id=3D"0119bd7367d1">Enable SNOW Teams integration for approvals (<=
strong>Aleksei</strong>): <a class=3D"external-link" data-card-appearance=
=3D"inline" href=3D"https://www.servicenow.com/docs/r/yokohama/employee-ser=
vice-management/employee-experience-foundation/actionable-notifications.htm=
l" local-id=3D"0430f4451b79" rel=3D"nofollow">https://www.servicenow.com/do=
cs/r/yokohama/employee-service-management/employee-experience-foundation/ac=
tionable-notifications.html</a></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8d6f3184c915">
<p local-id=3D"59910ab17835">Update SNOW Approval workflow directly (<stron=
g>Aleksei</strong>): <a class=3D"external-link" data-card-appearance=3D"inl=
ine" href=3D"https://www.servicenow.com/community/developer-forum/trigger-a=
pproval-notification-for-every-24hrs-if-no-action-taken/m-p/2652516" local-=
id=3D"0a1fee57545e" rel=3D"nofollow">https://www.servicenow.com/community/d=
eveloper-forum/trigger-approval-notification-for-every-24hrs-if-no-action-t=
aken/m-p/2652516</a></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d36b49f3e82c">
<p local-id=3D"0e4a682c70a7">Dispatch Gopher agents to stimulate approvers =
using Power Automate (<strong>Nakatsu</strong>-san)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8644d23f0e8c">
<p local-id=3D"b39cb9f16107"><strong>Setup Gopher</strong> to annoy ETS Jap=
an - Keni, Birger (Nakatsu)</p>
<ul local-id=3D"6e8a265e5b4f">
<li local-id=3D"3f0a40c6-eefe-4b53-b6fe-56985a4ac77d">
<p local-id=3D"830609f1dad6">Teams, email 2x / day</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ebf9e4bf-ac05-4d34-a15f-eb56e7d6849a">
<p local-id=3D"a40bec0ff369">Add manager after 24 hours</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper c=
